Penalties/Disadvantages 
-------------------------------------------
Cannot wear helmet due to cybernetic eyelink being in the way.
Cannot wield anything but guns or bare fists.
Must spend money on Ammo constantly.

Powers
-------------------------------------------
Scan - Provides information on opponents defenses.
Higher % of critical hit with levels.
Breech- Can give a weapon +1 per every 10 levels.  Only for own use.
Headshot - Attempt a finishing critical hit.
